MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- IntroLoader with two swappable animations via ANIMATION_TYPE constant:
  'typography' → letters elastic bounce + elevator gate split
  'fill'       → text fill progress + curtain slide up
- HeroSection accepts ready prop — waits for intro to complete
- Page reveal sequence: Navbar slideDown → Badge → H1 line1 → H1 line2 → Subtitle
- All animations use power4.out for premium feel
- Dynamic GSAP import — zero bundle impact on initial load
